#X text 39 8 When in edit mode \, [knob] shows its inlet/outlet. The inlet will always be hidden if you have a receive symbol \, same with the outlet if you have a send symbol. You can set a send symbol above to send messages to a matching [receive] object. A receive symbol makes [send] objects communicate to it., f 48;
